    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty car, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can definitely count on it for all your weekend trips or the daily commute. Everything runs smoothly, and it's just waiting for a new owner to take it on some fresh adventures! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
